data.description: Beautiful residence offers innate charm and great style. The interior features an open floor plan with expansive windows for natural light, multiple living areas, fantastic kitchen, breakfast bar, pantry, inviting dining area and privately situated master suite located downstairs. The outdoor space is complete with a covered porch and deck for entertaining. This home offers convenience to restaurants and shopping and is located in a desirable neighborhood with amenities including a community pool.
